Package: TaxaHabitat
Type: Package
Title: Habitat Assignment and Spatial Quality Control for Taxonomic Occurrences
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kevin", "Lafferty", , "klafferty@usgs.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Assigns habitat classifications to taxonomic occurrence records
    using LLM prompts and performs spatial quality control. Receives occurrence
    data from TaxaFetch and produces habitat-annotated, spatially screened
    records for input to TaxaExpect. Part of the TaxaID ecosystem.
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
